channel.title: Need Help - Client Compiling
channel.description:
Ive Downloaded Deathzscape's Client but they're all .class files.
I decompiled the client.java 'coz he has the port as 43595. But when I change the port to 43594 and compile, it says this...
[code]client.java:6236: illegal start of expression aClass30_Sub2_Sub4_Sub1_Sub2_1126 = this.aClass30_Sub2_Sub4_Sub1_Sub2Array890[this.anInt889] = = new Class30_Sub2_Sub4_Sub1_Sub2();
^ client.java:7070: '.class' expected label626: int i14; ^ client.java:7070: not a statement label626: int i14; ^ 3 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Any help please?
Thanks in advance.
